{
  "texts": [
    "AI-generated clinical images are discouraged unless part of formal research.",
    "Authors are accountable for AIgenerated content, and peer reviewers must not input manuscripts into AI tools, with any assistance disclosed.",
    "These policies stress accountability, confidentiality, and human oversight, aligning with ICMJE and COPE guidelines to ensure ethical AI use in publishing.",
    "Humans must consider the privacy risks and personal data implications of AI tools.",
    "Increasing reliance on AI raises concerns about younger generations losing critical assessment skills, potentially affecting scientific integrity."
  ]
}